<!-- SC_OFF --><div class="md"><p><a href="https://chess.com">chess.com</a> forces you to create a ticket to even request this.</p> <blockquote> <p>We try to reply within 1-2 business days, but can sometimes get backed up with holidays or lots of inquiries. </p> </blockquote> <p>Beware before entering your payment information into <a href="https://chess.com">chess.com</a></p> <p>The only way other way to remove it seems to be to completely delete your account. Similarly, the billing page listed <a href="https://support.chess.com/article/500-how-can-i-update-my-credit-card-information-on-chesscom#:%7E:text=You%20can%20update%20your%20credit,on%20the%20Account%2FPayment%20option.&amp;text=Here%20you%20can%20change%20the,plan%20at%20the%20membership%20page">here</a> links to a page on <a href="https://chess.com">chess.com</a> that contains no information or option to delete.</p> </div><!-- SC_ON --> &#32; submitted by &#32; <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Eternal_Nexus"> /u/Eternal_Nexus </a> <br/> <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/chess/comments/wc9038/beware_it_is_impossible_to_delete_your_credit/">[link]</a></span> &#32; <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/chess/comments/wc9038/beware_it_is_impossible_to_delete_your_credit/">[comments]</a></span>